DataElement.preferredDefinition: A substance made from living organisms or things they produce. EXAMPLE(S): virus, therapeutic serum, toxin, antitoxin, vaccine, blood, blood component or derivative, allergenic product, analogous product The date (and time), assigned by the manufacturer, on which the product should not be used.
